high_descs: Turn around and go near the dining table.
Take the pot from the dining table.
Turn around and go near the fridge.
Take it out and go near the dining table.
Put the pot on the dining table.
anns.task_desc: Placed the pot on the dining table.

high_descs: Turn right and go through the door to exit the room, then left and go all the way down the hall until reaching the wall, then turn left to the table in the kitchen area.
Pick up the pot from the table.
Approach the pink fridge next to the table.
Put the pot in the fridge, let it cool, then remove it.
Turn back to the table you got the pot from.
Put the pot back down on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooled pot on a dining table.

high_descs: Go toward the door and turn left and go to the dining table.
Pick up the pot from the dining table.
Place the pot in the fridge then, take the pot out of the fridge.
Turn around to the dining table.
Place the pot on the dining table.
anns.task_desc: Place a cool pot on the dining table.
